517
00:31:11,327 --> 00:31:14,498
Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them.

518
00:31:14,581 --> 00:31:17,709
-Harry Potter?
-It's the same world, but new.

519
00:31:18,585 --> 00:31:20,671
-I wanted to see that.
-That sounds good!

520
00:31:20,754 --> 00:31:22,548
-I want to see it.
-It was really good.

521
00:31:22,631 --> 00:31:24,340
Yeah, the movie was good.

522
00:31:24,425 --> 00:31:26,468
-Entertaining?
-It was.

523
00:31:27,135 --> 00:31:30,096
How was Yusuke?
What was he like?

524
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:35,351
He asked if I wanted to have dinner after.

525
00:31:35,436 --> 00:31:38,689
To go have dinner with him.

526
00:31:38,772 --> 00:31:43,652
But I told him it's Friday
and my grandma cooked already

527
00:31:43,735 --> 00:31:45,404
so I was going to have dinner with her.

528
00:31:45,487 --> 00:31:46,572
And that was it.

529
00:31:46,655 --> 00:31:49,533
-So it was just the movie?
-Yeah, just the movie.

530
00:31:49,616 --> 00:31:53,829
We didn't talk much
since we were in a movie theater.

531
00:31:54,538 --> 00:31:55,831
That's how it went.

532
00:31:58,417 --> 00:32:00,001
Are you okay?

533
00:32:00,752 --> 00:32:05,090
